679
00:37:50,517 --> 00:37:54,604
So I pulled Sanchez and Ruiz
outta retirement.

680
00:37:54,688 --> 00:37:57,023
I had 'em working on the outside,
you know?

681
00:37:57,357 --> 00:37:59,943
