689
00:38:21,131 --> 00:38:22,966
That's where the real files are.

690
00:38:23,049 --> 00:38:25,677
Everything you need
to exterminate these rat fucks.

691
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,803
It's in there!

692
00:38:26,928 --> 00:38:29,389
You're gonna have to finish
